                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8489" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2137</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1088 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“虎牙”要冬眠了吗？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is&quot;HUYA&quot;going to hibernate?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佘震宇，丁进</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州虎牙信息科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">虎牙直播；盈利模式；商业模式；创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HUYA Live；Profit Model；Business Model；Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">互联网直播是近些年的热门行业，而游戏直播则是该行业的重要分支。虎牙直播是游戏直播企业的代表，更是在“千播大战”中，突出重围，赴海外上市。自创立以来，虎牙一直努力提升直播技术、强化内外部管理和发展多项业务，软硬实力都得到巨大提升。但是由于自身业务过分垂直和经营环境变化等等原因，虎牙近年来面临着盈利困境。本案例重点讲述了虎牙直播构建盈利优势、拓展盈利来源、创新并优化盈利模式和完善商业模式的措施和历程。通过对本案例的学习，希望学生能够在纵观虎牙直播发展历程的基础上，思考虎牙直播盈利模式的构成、变化和弊端，深入理解盈利模式及商业模式；同时结合对虎牙直播的案例理解，对垂直类平台提出相关建议，掌握并运用相关理论，解决实际问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Internet live broadcasting is a hot industry in recent years, and game live broadcasting is an important branch of this industry. HUYA Live is a representative of gaming live streaming companies, and has emerged victorious in the era of the &quot;thousand broadcast war&quot; by going public overseas. Since its establishment, HUYA has been striving to enhance its live streaming technology, strengthen internal and external management, and develop multiple businesses, resulting in significant improvements in both software and hardware capabilities. However, due to its overly vertical business and changes in the operating environment, HUYA has faced profitability difficulties in recent years.This case focuses on the measures and processes taken by HUYA Live to build profit advantages, expand profit sources, innovate and optimize profit models, and improve business models. Through the study of this case, it is hoped that students can reflect on the composition, changes, and drawbacks of HUYA&#39;s profit model based on a comprehensive overview of its development process, and gain a deeper understanding of profit and business models; At the same time, based on the case study of HUYA Live, provide relevant suggestions for vertical platforms, master and apply relevant theories, and solve practical problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“微笑曲线”理论、五要素模型、服务利润链理论、魏朱商业模式六要素理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-08</td>
                            </tr>
